episodes.title: Shugden/Dolgyal Controversy and Personal Experiences - Carol I/V
episodes.description: The wonderful and brave, lovely Carol McQuire talking about her life in the NKT after our small information handout on October 5th in London.

episodes.title: Shugden/Dolgyal Controversy and Personal Experiences - Linda I/V
episodes.description: The wonderful and brave, lovely Linda talking about her life in the NKT after our small information handout on October 5th in London. Please applaud her - she's the first 'survivor' speaking on video to the public - historic!
